00:03:49.500 --> 00:03:54.667
 LaGG-3's sophisticated weapons and good maneuverability make it easier to deal with such battles. 

00:03:54.900 --> 00:03:56.100
 Let's summarize 

00:03:56.200 --> 00:03:59.100
 LaGG-3 is a very well controlled aircraft 

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:05.167
 With a wide selection of components, players can choose any tactic they like while maintaining good mobility. 

00:04:05.267 --> 00:04:10.700
 This adaptability makes LaGG-3 successful against almost all of the same class aircraft. 

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:16.900
 If you are still not sure which branch you want to study, today the protagonist of our story will help you make the right choice. 

